# Parcel package
- Local Server
- Dev build
- Hot module replacement
- Production build
- File watching algorithm ( keeps an eye on the files and only rebuilds the ones that have changed )
- Faster build because of caching
- Bundling
- Image optimisation
- Minification 
- Differential bundling
- Code splitting
- Tree shaking !

# Redux toolkit
- Install @reduxjs/toolkit and react-redux
- Build our store
- Connect sotre to app
- Create card slice
- Dispatch action
- read data using selector

# Testing app
- Install react testing library
- Install jest
- Install babel dependencies
- Configure babel
- Configure parcel config to disable default babel transpilation as parcel uses babel already
- Jest - nox jest --init
- Install jsdom library
- Install @babel/preset-react so jsx ( react files ) are configured for jest.
- npm i -D @testing-library/jest-dom
